"""Test 41-species forcing output"""
_, F41, _ = fair.forward.fair_scm(emissions=rcp85.Emissions.emissions,
    efficacy=np.ones(41), diagnostics='AR6')
_, F13, _ = fair.forward.fair_scm(emissions=rcp85.Emissions.emissions,
    efficacy=np.ones(13))
assert np.allclose(F41.sum(axis=1), F13.sum(axis=1))
